做就不用怕，自然大把人撐！</blockquote><br />\n屌你講呀<br />\n上次屌鳩個廢老打尖<br />\n之後個廢老排左係我後面就算<br />\n明明後面仲有幾十人<br />\n無人岀聲無人幫口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人就係鍾意食花生睇好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚死會比人拍片放上網咁</blockquote><br />\n香港人最撚怕事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃撚圾黎<br />\n仲要全部男人老狗<br />\n有老有嫩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分分鐘有班正義c9衝出黎屌鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗起祥興記比人偷野食<br />\nFb 班人仲慷他人之慨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df7ee2a6d9b380f13fba1c10a223b3eb17f526b","tid":328613,"uid":4285,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:31:55.000Z","msg":"我日日舉鐵都係為左搭地鐵撞開人<br />\n<br />\n撞完, 佢地見你大大隻隻, 又唔敢出聲 <br />\n<br />\n好爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aef5a9d5348c6adbd3b4ad2f511b1556c465b8c","tid":328613,"uid":106130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:47:56.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"},{"pid":"476cb3e286558855c9ed8ced61e482fe99c602a5","tid":328613,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實你真係幾on9, 同冇撚用，1st我唔認為係咪癈老，做出呢個行為我會直接屌柒佢，開拖都唔係味試過，排隊係正確的，敢做就不用怕，自然大把人撐！</blockquote><br />\n阻到佢上車係最好嘅結果</blockquote><br />\n咪就係， 平時左膠泛民都多野講， 結果無樣做得成"},{"pid":"f395ae2231366612a755d4cd28c4c6c382f0af3c","tid":328613,"uid":46700,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲廢老就係咁仆街<br />\n成日以為自己大曬就亂嚟<br />\n咁有力水打尖就更加唔應該讓<br />\n香港啲同情心就係因為呢種人搞到冇曬"},{"pid":"6861e17ebce62df3514483fded51b89e9279b409","tid":328613,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:02:03.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fab5649d68d806cf99105cc83418044b67a586d","tid":328613,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:03:58.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded49fe52759fd08a28e5db2917ff377bd06a464","tid":328613,"uid":25781,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"打尖已經係閒事<br />\n好多廢老係直接自己開一條新龍<br />\n車一到就第一個狗衝上車<br />\n有次俾我一嘢撞開佢再帶後面班人上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實以前都有呢班唔撚跟隊嘅人<br />\n不過佢哋會有自知之明等排隊嘅人上哂車先再上<br />\n點解而家啲廢老可以咁撚無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab271ad14f62bfdd9e8052ec94a61fd3bcae5a29","tid":328613,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:08:13.000Z","msg":"做得好，岀街見到啲老野就好忟，好想打7啲廢老！"},{"pid":"bc4a70e642ad050e61aab70662186418b08b9334","tid":328613,"uid":46624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736f341c657b431c92bf686b7e90091fc8eb072f","tid":328613,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:09:23.000Z","msg":"ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb599667270cfa9abebdf39ce0675e81efd9c5f9","tid":328613,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:25:09.000Z","msg":"其實「有需要人士」係咪攞正牌可以打尖？<br />\n<br />\n巴士站有「請先讓有需要人士上車」(大意)的字句。"},{"pid":"7723475926f28f148e2d8f07de98a7ed0cd6a08a","tid":328613,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02: