":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實你真係幾on9, 同冇撚用，1st我唔認為係咪癈老，做出呢個行為我會直接屌柒佢，開拖都唔係味試過，排隊係正確的，敢做就不用怕，自然大把人撐！</blockquote><br />\n屌你講呀<br />\n上次屌鳩個廢老打尖<br />\n之後個廢老排左係我後面就算<br />\n明明後面仲有幾十人<br />\n無人岀聲無人幫口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由佢<br />\n<br />\n佢唔打我尖我理撚得佢"},{"pid":"4a861d766f13556bf0cea0974ed8cd1848a8e327","tid":328613,"uid":17459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬做得好 同埋好彩無搞大件事<br />\n如果唔係廢老遲d 可以優先上車<br />\n<br />\n你知香港班報紙佬同議員都係偏幫廢老<br />\n一陣真係好似關愛座咁整條關愛隊就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw, 我見沙田有d 綠van 真係係部車貼住廢老同傷殘優先上車，屌你老味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n優佢老味咩<br />\n佢有佢優先座 我有我當佢普通座 邊忽優先？睇過？</blockquote><br />\n人人都係比錢撘車 讓座都要睇人肯唔肯啦<br />\n一係就整個關愛車比班廢老慢慢爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58858b8b48f15e0bda2b4937deb4e4191527d4e","tid":328613,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f22b8471812b08c2d109aff429999e5dcfc552","tid":328613,"uid":55419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:02:03.000Z","msg":"屌手快快想禁正皮點知禁左落負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cab726ed212d633b006e80ba141673dbe71af8b","tid":328613,"uid":8040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬做得好 同埋好彩無搞大件事<br />\n如果唔係廢老遲d 可以優先上車<br />\n<br />\n你知香港班報紙佬同議員都係偏幫廢老<br />\n一陣真係好似關愛座咁整條關愛隊就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw, 我見沙田有d 綠van 真係係部車貼住廢老同傷殘優先上車，屌你老味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n優佢老味咩<br />\n佢有佢優先座 我有我當佢普通座 邊忽優先？睇過？</blockquote><br />\n人人都係比錢撘車 讓座都要睇人肯唔肯啦<br />\n一係就整個關愛車比班廢老慢慢爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地後生對社會有貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  宜家我地後生應該回饋佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你，佢地搭車比$2， 其餘差價係政府比架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時專門坐過海巴士唔坐短途線，最後都係納稅人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd167f97a03f7f9b42891596e8c6e720ed959ea","tid":328613,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我日日舉鐵都係為左搭地鐵撞開人<br />\n<br />\n撞完, 佢地見你大大隻隻, 又唔敢出聲 <br />\n<br />\n好爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<br />\n<br />\n火車沙田落車 次次推開唔讓人落車廢老。<br />\n<br />\n尋日一腳踢開支那蝗個喼。加句屌你老母。個蝗開頭兇鳩返我。屌多佢兩句同我笑。<br />\n<br />\n支那蝗真係犯賤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c562e299b76ba57da0609d01554579722814ee33","tid":328613,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"我都試過比人攝 <br />\n推番佢出去 <br />\n山門<br />\n舉中指"},{"pid":"bff52b6c863f8ea50b3115ee3876020f32164394","tid":328613,"uid":5311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"通常我排第1位<br />\n後面好多人排 <br />\n但總有d 師奶廢老扮晒野 排我隔離<br />\n我就會頂q住佢唔俾上 等我後面d人上先<br />\n等佢冇位坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de903375cc87f1983eaf6104fae1c2945991c398","tid":328613,"uid":78539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:17:20.000Z","msg":"最憎D人 明明無位仲死迫入黎 個次返工 有條友係尖咀 死迫入黎 本身已經關唔到門 仲係咁迫 俾我一野推出去 再屌佢老味 佢咩住我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7a5dc9cc390a4422997c149e15801c11c6e2de","tid":328613,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:19:50.000Z","msg":"點解有1個負評？個廢老都有連登ac ?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19768e437cefef523beda204f2c6ef5fc36ea6d","tid":328613,"uid":49176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:41:32.000Z","msg":"其實排隔離唔一定錯喎"},{"pid":"fb209dcfd0a41b30c775a345ac4ac8a0b15b554b","tid":328613,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打尖已經係閒事<br />\n好多廢老係<span style=\"color: red;\">直接自己開一條新龍</span><br />\n車一到就第一個狗衝上車<br />\n有次俾我一嘢撞開佢再帶後面班人上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實以前都有呢班唔撚跟隊嘅人<br />\n不過佢哋會有自知之明等排隊嘅人上哂車先再上<br />\n點解而家啲廢老可以咁撚無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲多數企死喺中間落車位，啲人落車佢就夾硬衝上車<br />\n見到呢啲阿叔阿嬸我多數都企定喺度等佢，佢唔郁我就牙吓牙吓頂撚住佢唔比佢上車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後屌鳩佢「大陸人呀？唔識排隊呀！？」<br />\n最後頂到佢上唔到車為止"},{"pid":"f7cd7dcb48c63e56db9e06282bf3f30f9dfde0a6","tid":328613,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"睇下邊撚個死先？"},{"pid":"ba4dc4f5c231c3df2b97bea0ec419044864f58ea","tid":328613,"uid":48654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:11:48.000Z","msg":"班死廢老要人讓既同時，<br />\n有冇諗過自己幾撚冇品？<br />\n有品就自動有人尊敬，<br />\n佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3544919f20ff42a30e8e6c2e49c71fd05444e6","tid":328613,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:12:01.000Z","msg":"啱呀，唔洗畀面班人型畜牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為老不尊呀嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3068a90e2f64a8e69a386eece1265fe401c64a52","tid":328613,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:12:02.000Z","msg":"最撚火唔係個廢老攝位，而家望住啲門口狗廢物任佢攝，樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638840d8bdec549e5caec6d7eee660cad17d84fc","tid":328613,"uid":70491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"試過比人側位入，讓左半個身位，等條友入左條隊半個身位，以為有得上，門一開，扎衡馬頂翻條友出隊，結果後面一窩蜂跟住行，條友個樣由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5891ec3d1788aec283010591acb772dce633318c","tid":328613,"uid":3506,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:22:20.000Z","msg":"之前我都試過 <br />\n係九龍塘站 收工時間<br />\n啲廢老好鍾意係側面偷雞攝上嚟<br />\n我同你一樣個身打側頂撚住條柒頭<br />\n但後尾大家都上到車<br />\n上到車我捉實個扶手 條撚屌特登捉住同一條扶手<br />\n用手踭撞我 我屌佢老母我梗係唔執輸同佢鬥力<br />\n迫到佢冇力行後左一架步 同我講 對唔住 唔玩<br />\n心涼曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d92aca20199e3cf18e614818497122a5fc41232","tid":328613,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:32:32.000Z","msg":"樓主真英雄"},{"pid":"9bbfe5a02c9909511b55c3e10db52d6e22bd8f95","tid":328613,"uid":29684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做得好！班廢老應該全體槍斃！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d97a1cf00551a40487c3b7cf3a9080c80c57fd7","tid":328613,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:46:49.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1933572b2a88bf45